{"tid":398934,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［留學］寄嘢去英國，D表點填？","createTime":"2017-09-13T14:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T15:50:00.000Z","uid":144215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1632d8b1352a0cb8d4efb495c4d98d639dffdc8b","tid":398934,"uid":144215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"後日第一次飛英國讀書   <br />\n聽日去郵局寄兩箱特快<br />\n見官網寫話每樣嘢幾重幾多都要寫清楚<br />\n但我兩箱嘢裡面乜柒都有<br />\n想問下係咪真係要寫嘥落去<br />\n有冇巴絲有D方便D嘅寫法又唔會俾人沒收？"},{"pid":"3eeba4ea158f77acb1f54fefd64b369201395def","tid":398934,"uid":16120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:21:15.000Z","msg":"Gifts<br />\nPersonal belongings"},{"pid":"50e13f43765da8696e49c969f8895bcb1a8408f4","tid":398934,"uid":144215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gifts<br />\nPersonal belongings</blockquote><br />\n絲打自己係咁填？冇問題順利寄到？？"},{"pid":"f77d9bb85602a9c6ef0531267f696e8537926b7b","tid":398934,"uid":92589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:39:16.000Z","msg":"personal belongings 就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日啱啱寄完"},{"pid":"9cf323aa32eb2f2165d0c7b6eeab3d0e50fa5f30","tid":398934,"uid":92589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"舊年寄左好多次都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3f0b59b4b4dd0409b965fec30dae460f80dceb","tid":398934,"uid":16120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Gifts<br />\nPersonal belongings</blockquote><br />\n絲打自己係咁填？冇問題順利寄到？？</blockquote><br />\n正常應該唔會沒收<br />\n最多會hold 起箱野 再寄信比你話要打稅<br />\n<br />\n試過有件大褸未剪牌寄<br />\n比海關hold 起左<br />\n比完錢(稅) 就放返出黎<br />\n<br />\n之後寫信比海關話 邊件貨 邊個tracking no. Reference no. D野係自用<br />\n讀完書離開英國就會拎返走 唔會拎去賣<br />\n就可以退返D稅<br />\n<br />\n呢次之後次次寄個陣 申報寫personal belongings 都暢通無阻"},{"pid":"2da665cd4d16bf0d6b0505db422246357ad0e222","tid":398934,"uid":130394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:12:36.000Z","msg":"連登仔真係乜柒嘢都要上網問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用下你個腦啦. 去外國讀書仲要問呢啲咁垃圾嘅問題. 寫日常用品咪得囉"},{"pid":"80795bce14859dfb5a97933e4443dc1c372862d6","tid":398934,"uid":144215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:43:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Gifts<br />\nPersonal belongings</blockquote><br />\n絲打自己係咁填？冇問題順利寄到？？</blockquote><br />\n正常應該唔會沒收<br />\n最多會hold 起箱野 再寄信比你話要打稅<br />\n<br />\n試過有件大褸未剪牌寄<br />\n比海關hold 起左<br />\n比完錢(稅) 就放返出黎<br />\n<br />\n之後寫信比海關話 邊件貨 邊個tracking no. Reference no. D野係自用<br />\n讀完書離開英國就會拎返走 唔會拎去賣<br />\n就可以退返D稅<br />\n<br />\n呢次之後次次寄個陣 申報寫personal belongings 都暢通無阻</blockquote><br />\n唔該嘥絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a9972c608e09f47d10e8f8fbf63c7156e818e0","tid":398934,"uid":144215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T15:50:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊年寄左好多次都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}